Class Queue<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.ldaptive.pool.Queue<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - type of object in the queue
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Iterable<T>
    public class Queue<T>
extends Object
implements Iterable<T>
    Provides a wrapper around a Deque to support LIFO and FIFO operations.
